    "description": "The inspiration for this recipe comes from Poulet Yassa, a chicken dish from the Casamance region of Southern Senegal. You'll marinate chicken and onions in lots of citrus (ideally overnight if you can!), before creating a lemony-Dijon mustard sauce with caramelised onions and peppers to serve.",
